text: Nathaniel Caleb Atkinson (born 13 June 1999) is an Australian soccer player. He plays for Heart of Midlothian in the Scottish Premiership and for the Australia men's national soccer team (nicknamed the "Socceroos"). ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Australian men's soccer players Category:Sportspeople from Launceston, Tasmania Category:2022 FIFA World Cup players
